  id: Terminology
  title: Terminology
  author: BCMGF1137
  description: 'This is the sixth module I''ve uploaded so far, good luck!


    Determine the word corresponding to its definition in the Merriam-Webster Dictionary,
    and identify the one displayed module where its manual contains that word.


    ///


    Realistically speaking, this should have come out a month ago. I got demotivated
    due to thinking the module was not really satisfying to do when you''re advanced,
    but I still liked the concept anyway, and it''s pretty soloable when you study
    it hard enough lol. Enjoy!

    Oh yeah, and there''s Twitch Plays support inside...'
